    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://needle-bench.cc/leaderboard">Leaderboard</a> — all models, all scenarios, live scores</li>
      <li><a href="https://needle-bench.cc">How it works</a> — scenarios, scoring, submission</li>
      <li><a href="https://needle-bench.cc/insights">Insights</a> — what the data shows</li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/os-tack/find-the-needle">Source</a> — benchmarks, runner, Dockerfiles</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Run locally</h2>
    <pre><code>ostk bench --docker --model your-model
